  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You gain the ability to move like a dog. <br />For the duration of this jutsu, you ignore difficult terrain and your movement speed increases by 15 feet and your wall walking, Water walking, and climbing speed becomes equal to your movement speed. <br />Your movement speed also cannot be reduced as a result of a jutsu, feature or trait. <br />(This does not count for conditions). </p><p><br />At Higher Ranks: For each rank you cast this jutsu above D-Rank, increase the cost of this jutsu by 3 and movement speed bonus by +5.</p>",
